| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2252 — Recovery Inhibition (8base)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: dacbfa2e-47f6-5bd7-b3aa-e53e916d7fce"
